ine giving subscribers access to information on home design trend and tips the company was founded by delia fischer georg biersack tim schäfer matthias siepe alan poensgehn benno zerlin and stefan smalla in  and is headquartered in munich germany details hidden oxford nanopore technologies ltd oxford nanopore technologies ltd develops proprietary technology platform for the electronic analysis of single molecules it also develops instruments like gridiontm and miniontm which are adaptable for the analysis of dna rna proteins small molecules and other types of molecule the firms platform has a broad range of potential applications including scientific research personalized medicine crop science and security and defence the company was founded by gordon sanghera spike willcocks and john hagan pryce bayley in  and is headquartered in oxford the united kingdom details hidden kgb text uk ltd kgb text uk ltd provided mobile applications and information services it offered answers for questions on various topics including travel restaurants shopping health music and sports the company was founded by sarah mcvittie and thomas roberts in august  and is headquartered in cambridge the united kingdom holdings  top positions restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ odey asset management × search close fund company odey asset management  httpwwwodeycom   odey asset management is a leading london investment firm managing c bn for institutional investors private banks  individual investors across global  european strategies  the firm was established by crispin odey in  to focus on active fund management with an equal emphasis on preserving capital and generating superior returns odey have worked hard to build an investment team and a client base committed to these principles and today continue to focus on performance and not asset gathering more than half of their  employees are investment professionals and the partners are amongst the largest investors in the strategies they run in  the odey wealth management was launched to deliver a portfolio management service in addition to their investment funds in  odey embarked on a joint venture with bruellan wealth management a swiss asset management firm serving high net worth individuals to bring odey asset managements investment knowhow to the swiss market company fund name isin currency inception date rating risk profile odey asset management llp odey opportunity fund usd cap iebgbx usd   high the investment objective of the subfund is to achieve capital appreciation through investment on a global basis including in emerging markets in a diversified portfolio of investments as set out below odey asset management llp odey invest fd plc odey opp fd cap iebwhmv gbp   high the investment objective of the subfund is to achieve capital appreciation through investment on a global basis including in emerging markets in a diversified portfolio of investments as set out below odey asset management llp odey inv fd plc odey opp fd eur cap iebwmd eur   medium the investment objective of the subfund is to achieve capital appreciation through investment on a global basis including in emerging markets in a diversified portfolio of investments as set out below odey asset management llp capita cf odey continental european cap gb gbp   low the investment objective of this fund is to achieve long term capital appreciation through investing primarily in quoted securities issued by companies with principal offices in continental europe and the normal policy of the fund is to invest in a broad spread of equities but the fund may also invest in government bonds other fixed interest securities and preferred stocks if in the opinion of the manager and the investment manager this is appropriate to the goal of maximising capital growth     odey asset management llp private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of odey asset management llp snapshot people company overview odey asset management llp is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor the firm provides its services to institutional investors it launches and manages equity fixed income and balanced mutual funds for its clients the firm manages separate client focused long only strategy it also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients the firm invests in the public equity fixed income and hedging markets across the globe it employs a fundamental analysis to create its portfolios the firm conducts inhouse research to make its investments odey asset management llp was founded in  and is based in london  upper grosvenor streetlondon  wk ndunited kingdomfounded in  phone     fax     wwwodeycouk key executives for odey asset management llp mr robin crispin william odey founding partner chief investment officer head of investment management and portfolio manager age  mr tim michael pearey chief financial officer chief operating officer partner and director mr david mark george fletcher chairman alternate director ceo and partner age  mr rajesh chaudhary partner and senior analyst hon ralph daniel beckett director of trading and partner compensation as of fiscal year  odey asset management llp key developments odey asset management llp presents at morningstar investment conference  london  may  am apr   odey asset management llp presents at morningstar investment conference  london  may  am venue park plaza riverbank hotel london united kingdom speakers oliver james st goar kelton partner portfolio manager and associate director odey